59\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-3959\" alt=\"34-Specify Database Engine authentication security mode-Add current user\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/34-specify-database-engine-authentication-security-mode-add-current-user-1.jpg?w=660\" width=\"660\" height=\"493\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>After installation complete, open <strong>SQL Server Management Studio<\/strong> and click on the instance name and choose <strong>Properties<\/strong>, choose\u00a0<strong>Memory,\u00a0<\/strong>enter <strong>4000<\/strong> as <strong>Minimum<\/strong> and <strong>Maximum<\/strong> server memory, it&#8217;s\u00a0recommended\u00a0to be <strong>8000<\/strong>.<a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2013\/03\/11\/installing-system-center-configuration-manager-2012-sp1-on-windows-server-2012\/34-2-set-minimum-and-maximum-server-memory-for-sql-server\/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3958\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-3958\" alt=\"34-2-Set Minimum and Maximum server memory for SQL Server\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/34-2-set-minimum-and-maximum-server-memory-for-sql-server-1.jpg?w=660\" width=\"660\" height=\"534\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#339966;\"><strong>Download and install Assessment and Deployment Kit<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>Download <a title=\"Assessment and Deployment Kit\" href=\"http:\/\/msdn.microsoft.com\/en-us\/library\/windows\/hardware\/hh825420.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Assessment and Deployment Kit<\/a>, for download click <a title=\"Download\" href=\"http:\/\/www.microsoft.com\/en-eg\/download\/details.aspx?id=34866\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>\u00a0after that\u00a0click on <strong>adksetup<\/strong>.<a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2013\/03\/11\/installing-system-center-configuration-manager-2012-sp1-on-windows-server-2012\/35-download-and-run-assessment-and-deployment-kit\/#ma